trans-unit.source: Represents a content anchor or cargo resource for an <xref href="System.Windows.Annotations.Annotation"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Representa um recurso de âncora ou carga de conteúdo de um <xref href="System.Windows.Annotations.Annotation"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: AnnotationResource elements are used to model <xref:System.Windows.Annotations.Annotation.Anchors%2A> (the data that is being annotated) and <xref:System.Windows.Annotations.Annotation.Cargos%2A> (the data provided by the user such as a text note) in an <xref:System.Windows.Annotations.Annotation>.
trans-unit.target: Elementos de AnnotationResource são usados para o modelo <xref:System.Windows.Annotations.Annotation.Anchors%2A>(os dados que está sendo anotados) e <xref:System.Windows.Annotations.Annotation.Cargos%2A>(os dados fornecidos pelo usuário, como uma anotação de texto) em <xref:System.Windows.Annotations.Annotation>.</xref:System.Windows.Annotations.Annotation> </xref:System.Windows.Annotations.Annotation.Cargos%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Annotations.Annotation.Anchors%2A>

trans-unit.source: Through the use of <xref:System.Windows.Annotations.AnnotationResource.ContentLocators%2A> an AnnotationResource can refer to the content, directly contain the content, or both.
trans-unit.target: Com o uso de <xref:System.Windows.Annotations.AnnotationResource.ContentLocators%2A>um AnnotationResource pode se referir ao conteúdo, conter diretamente o conteúdo, ou ambos.</xref:System.Windows.Annotations.AnnotationResource.ContentLocators%2A>
